,"msg":"首先有無喪插先<br />\n唔係話佢啲咖喱唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fc59a474e063dfd746744fce15b90d78162706","tid":1823803,"uid":23634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:02:23.000Z","msg":"連登仔言論=暴徒意見？<br />\n連登仔幾時變左暴徒？"},{"pid":"54aef2f7cf69bcb0c2b1c6360081a5e769dcf5f1","tid":1823803,"uid":34553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c37d2164a528223b5be1d7140e067f5408820eab","tid":1823803,"uid":187232,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b46e2a8b31e7f87336168ae2fbce1a1ed5660ca5","tid":1823803,"uid":168250,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T03:43:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">泛暴派</span></span></strong>知咩料喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T03:45:07.000Z","msg":"仲有「煽暴派」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:03:56.000Z","msg":"重有縱暴派"},{"pid":"9cc64558890ad62c3873cde4fdacd0e70a9f5933","tid":1823803,"uid":225130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:20:01.000Z","msg":"唔做好食物質素仲要開分店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}